{"tid":1828980,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"當私隱署冇到！藍絲包圍港台 發起人聲言公開邱騰華電話號碼","createTime":"2020-01-18T10:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T11:11:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cc61419c0937acb07baa498f0808e944a812bd46","tid":1828980,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"香港政研會發起「天下圍公2」圍堵港台活動，百多人到場支持。在場有數十名軍裝警員以及便衣警員維持秩序，部份有佩戴委任證。眾人要求廣播處長梁家榮直接與他們見面，若不達成會發起「天下圍公3」，直接包圍處長。政研會主席鄧德成更公然要脅將港台高層等人起底及公開其電話，「我哋投訴不只於今日，會發動網上一人一電郵，一人一電話！我哋將會公開（廣播）處長、邱騰華局長、管理事務（通訊事務管理局）主席譚允芝電話，一齊打電話同佢傾傾偈！」<br />\n<br />\n去年8月政研會的「天下圍公」行動，號召數百名自稱撐警愛國人士圍堵港台，當日多間傳媒記者及攝影師成為被攻擊對象，被在場人士群起辱罵「黑記、做雞」等字眼，亦有記者被打及扯爛隨身物品。今次活動開始前，警察已在兩旁行人路設置鐵馬，亦有便衣女警不停呼籲馬路上的人士站回行人路。<br />\n<br />\n在場聲援人士多次辱罵港台為「曱甴電台」，活動未開始前，鄧已開咪向支持者稱：「如果有啲疑似記者嘅人對你哋不禮貌，唔好接受佢哋挑釁好無！」惟最終整個活動並沒有發生相關情況。大會工作人員向在場人士派發與新聞稿相近的一紙投訴信，逐個收集簽名。鄧指，有6萬人聯署香港電台改革是「主流民意」，包括要求辭退不稱職記者及工作人員、成立收視問責制度等，若港台不答應，將於2月份發動包圍廣播處長私人居所行動。<br />\n<br />\n在場人士多次指港台沒有收視，但事實上載至Youtube及facebook的港台節目，例如聚焦721元朗暴徒襲擊巿民事件的鏗鏘集，已有逾百多萬觀看人次。<br />\n<br />\n鄧又指，因商經局局長邱騰華局長指上次他們「萬人包圍行動」不算投訴所以無法跟進，故今次改為一人一信投訴，並反對增加港台撥款，更自稱是「主流民意」，「佢哋一日未改革，都唔應該增加撥款！」他指港台收視低至零時，更有現場女性尖叫歡呼，又指要求辭退利君雅及陳妙玲，因二人均曾在警方記者會上追問警方。其後港台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀出門接信，示威者在中午12左右散去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fE8669lP5phEfei0vksHVlKmrFE=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PJTACFD4LRA5YDQJREWLF6LBQU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FfE8669lP5phEfei0vksHVlKmrFE%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPJTACFD4LRA5YDQJREWLF6LBQU.png&h=9f70f8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/LuLxImJnzHYqljnIPu67SwJiSaQ=/802x601/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/45ZWFAKS44IGQZ4L6VLKYOBRZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FLuLxImJnzHYqljnIPu67SwJiSaQ%3D%2F802x601%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F45ZWFAKS44IGQZ4L6VLKYOBRZE.jpg&h=f2752c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200118/large/1579325187_73b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200118%2Flarge%2F1579325187_73b2.jpg&h=87712f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200118/3T26VT4XU3XN4NL3Z3IDTPVL3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200118%2F3T26VT4XU3XN4NL3Z3IDTPVL3E%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=64d02f29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200118%2F3T26VT4XU3XN4NL3Z3IDTPVL3E%2F&h=53c365f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200118/3T26VT4XU3XN4NL3Z3IDTPVL3E/</a>"},{"pid":"3315e77dfde104dea5f2e671fedc93178a591d9f","tid":1828980,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"係時候黃轉藍展示獸性既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd459da9210fd04f8df4ee51ba943f940d29bb1","tid":1828980,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"好呀"},{"pid":"9dbba98e95c9ccbd650ed0b51f74cfca3c1c49b6","tid":1828980,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T10:52:30.000Z","msg":"你咪公開囉，WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9cc4cc28d259ebae1ac7eafba73e57390d7a49","tid":1828980,"uid":146074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"到底點解港台咁硬"}]}